  06 Feb 2015; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild,
  +files/backlite-1.0.3-ffmpeg2.patch:
  fix build with ffmpeg2, bug #515160. patch grabbed from k9copy ebuild

  31 Dec 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Enforce USE dependency for media-libs/phonon.

  01 Mar 2014; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Depend on media-video/ffmpeg instead of virtual/ffmpeg. See bug #443192.

  28 Sep 2013; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Depend on dev-qt/qtdbus. This fixes bug #484162. Thanks to Nikoli for the
  report.

  10 Jul 2013; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Fixing qtgui deps for qt-4.8.5

  04 Mar 2013; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Switch to EAPI 5.

  02 Mar 2013; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Move Qt dependencies to the new category

  24 Jan 2013; Daniel Pielmeier <billie@gentoo.org> -backlite-1.0.3.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  22 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #451276

  17 Jan 2013; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild,
  +files/backlite-1.0.3-ffmpeg-0.11.patch,
  +files/backlite-1.0.3-includepaths.patch:
  Fix build with recent ffmpeg versions: Import patch from slackware and
  sanitize the include paths so that libavutil headers do not pollute it. Part
  of bug #443192

  13 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> backlite-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #451276

